From 7c702b4e35e2550c63e40e3d6f770d65b8c88d32 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Cursor Agent <cursoragent@cursor.com>
Date: Wed, 25 Feb 2026 00:32:35 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Put Allocator first in Result tuple: (Allocator,
 SpendBundleConditions)

Swap the tuple order in the return type of run_block_generator and
run_block_generator2 from Result<(SpendBundleConditions, Allocator), ...>
to Result<(Allocator, SpendBundleConditions), ...>, putting the allocator
first. Updated all call sites across the codebase to match.
